items.consumable

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • items.Item
      • items.consumable.Log
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Log
extends Item
    This class represents logs. Log type items are used to light a fire. They have a duration, which indicates how much time will a fire made with them persist.

      • use

        public int use()
        This method makes use of a number of logs specified by the constant LOGS_REQUIRED_FOR_A_FIRE. When used, logs start a fire.
        Specified by:
        use in class Item
        Returns:
        the number of logs used to light the fire, specified in the constant LOGS_REQUIRED_FOR_A_FIRE, or 0 if the fire couldn't be started.
